author: patrickl
msg: Modify LaunchFilter interface and modify LaunchTask.execute() to use the new LauncherCommand class to prevent LauncherFilter subclasses from changing the LaunchTask's cached values. With this change, LauncherFilter subclasses only can change temporary working copies of the cached values.
